Out of nowhere, a white Bengal tiger jumps down right in front of Antagony, 
transforms and looks like Tigatron. except its a female! "Scram Antagony, I 
am Snow Stalker and I will blow you away you predicon if you do not leave," 
Snow Stalker warns as she waves both guns in front of the female predicon.

>around. She saw that the base was very impressive, but the life on this

>little
